            <title>[PIG-3057] Make PigStorage.readField() protected</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3057</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;for the cases when we need to extend PigStorage just to override readField. Currently, we need to copy/paste several private fields and all getNext&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve changed readField from private to protected and added a new method: protected void addToCurrentTuple(DataByteArray data) &lt;/p&gt;</description>
